[warn]  ttnn.topk (sampling)                             vocab_size=64003         multi-core top-k requires vocab to be a power of 2 AND < 65536; else falls back to single-core
        fix: No action needed - kernel will use the single-core path. Decode
        throughput will be lower.
[warn]  ttnn.transformer.scaled_dot_product_attention (sliding) sliding_window=128       sliding-window attention is not supported in combination with chunked prefill
        fix: If using long-context prefill, disable chunked prefill for
        sliding-window layers.
[info]  ttnn.embedding                                   vocab_size=64003         vocab tile-padding: pads to multiple of 32 (no defect, just memory overhead if vocab is odd)
        fix: No action - padding is automatic, costs at most one tile per shard.

